metadata.description: Hood Apes is a collection of 10,000 unique well-designed Apes united together on the Ethereum Blockchain. Each Hood Ape is unique and exclusive based on 100+ traits. Entering into the Hood Apes community means joining a family full of investors and NFT enthusiasts who believe in the future of cryptocurrencies and blockchain technology.
